Setting System Bot Dialogs

System Bot Dialogs help guide the bot through the conversation flow, and you can assign custom dialogs as system dialogs to customize the experience.

To build and manage Einstein Bots:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

On the Dialogs panel, click  next to the dialog you wish to set as a System Bot Dialog.
Click Set as to define which system dialog to set.
